--== GRAPHSERVER CORE ==--

Build:
$ cd core
$ make

Install:
$ cd core
$ sudo make install

--== RUBY GRAPHSERVER ==--

Prerequisites:
Ruby 1.8.5

Build:
$ cd rbgs
Read the README

--== PYTHON GRAPHSERVER ==--

Prerequisites:
Python 2.6+ (or 2.5+ for only graphserver.core)

Build:
There is no build step!

Install and Test:
$ cd pygs
Read the README